TopicTitle: Hi! I'm new but not new

Articles.Content:
Hi!

I've been playing KSP for a while but have been kind of quiet about it. I decided to make a video of the first part of my "Duna quad-pack" adventure where I try to knock out four Duna related contracts at once. I haven't been to Duna before so packing for the trip had been interesting. If you've got any suggestions I'm more than interested ![:D](//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif)

<iframe width="480" height="270" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/dNa8qXtXkKw?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="true"></iframe>
Welcome! Duna is the first step to traveling to the outer planets.
Welcome aboard! I myself have only ever done one Dunar landing. That's all I ever really tried before, but now I think I'm gonna really try and gear up to go again.

I'm doing a mission to Duna right now, actually. Your video is looking cool, can't wait to see pt.2 ![:P](//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue.gif)

And also welcome
